		 HTML Include
		 ============

HTML Include handles Include files in HTML Source files. It checks
the given source file for certain Tags (special-styled comments) and
replace the content of the include area, if the content in the
associated include file was changed.

The full user manual is 'htinc.txt'


                Obtaining
                =========

HTML Included is hosted at BerliOS, at
http://developer.berlios.de/projects/htinc/

The home page is http://htinc.berlios.de

The Author is Robert Lange <robert.lange@s1999.tu-chemnitz.de>
